eqlControllerTable.name: eqlControllerTable
eqlControllerTable.description: EqualLogic-Dynamic Member Controller Table. This table contains controller status information. One table entry per controller. It is indexed by controller slot number. The number of entries is equal to the number of controllers that are present in the system

eqlControllerEntry.name: eqlControllerEntry
eqlControllerEntry.description: An entry (row) containing controller status information.

eqlControllerIndex.name: eqlControllerIndex
eqlControllerIndex.description: The index value that uniquely identifies the controller. It is equal to the controller slot number. The minimum slot number is 1

eqlControllerModel.name: eqlControllerModel
eqlControllerModel.description: This variable specifies controller model. Is value of Part=

eqlControllerCMRevision.name: eqlControllerCMRevision
eqlControllerCMRevision.description: CM version number; Is value of Rev=

eqlControllerSwRevision.name: eqlControllerSwRevision
eqlControllerSwRevision.description: This variable specifies the customer visible controller software revision.

eqlControllerBatteryStatus.name: eqlControllerBatteryStatus
eqlControllerBatteryStatus.description: This variable specifies controller battery status.

eqlControllerUpTime.name: eqlControllerUpTime
eqlControllerUpTime.description: This variable specifies time interval since the controller was last booted in seconds.

eqlControllerProcessorTemp.name: eqlControllerProcessorTemp
eqlControllerProcessorTemp.description: This variable specifies the temperature in Celsius.

eqlControllerChipsetTemp.name: eqlControllerChipsetTemp
eqlControllerChipsetTemp.description: This variable specifies the temperature in Celsius.

eqlControllerPrimaryOrSecondary.name: eqlControllerPrimaryOrSecondary
eqlControllerPrimaryOrSecondary.description: This variable specifies if the controller is a primary or secondary controller.

eqlControllerPrimaryFlashImageRev.name: eqlControllerPrimaryFlashImageRev
eqlControllerPrimaryFlashImageRev.description: The revision of the primary flash image.

eqlControllerSecondaryFlashImageRev.name: eqlControllerSecondaryFlashImageRev
eqlControllerSecondaryFlashImageRev.description: The revision of the secondary flash image.

eqlControllerSerialNumber.name: eqlControllerSerialNumber
eqlControllerSerialNumber.description: This variable specifies controller serial number. Is value of SN=

eqlControllerDate.name: eqlControllerDate
eqlControllerDate.description: This variable specifies date of mfg of the CM. Is value of Date=

eqlControllerECO.name: eqlControllerECO
eqlControllerECO.description: This variable specifies eco level of the CM. Is value of ECO=

eqlControllerPLDrev.name: eqlControllerPLDrev
eqlControllerPLDrev.description: This variable specifies pld version number.

eqlControllerPlatformType.name: eqlControllerPlatformType
eqlControllerPlatformType.description: This variable specifies the platform type. If the number is negative its a simulator. If zero its an eval platform. If >= 1 is the version of the pss board -- does this mean cm rev?

eqlControllerPlatformVersion.name: eqlControllerPlatformVersion
eqlControllerPlatformVersion.description: This variable specifies the version of the pss board (ie CM?)

eqlControllerCPUrev.name: eqlControllerCPUrev
eqlControllerCPUrev.description: This variable specifies the revision of the cpu.

eqlControllerCPUfreq.name: eqlControllerCPUfreq
eqlControllerCPUfreq.description: This variable specifies the cpu freq in MHz.

eqlControllerPhysRam.name: eqlControllerPhysRam
eqlControllerPhysRam.description: This variable specifies the amount of physical memory in MB.

eqlControllerBootRomVersion.name: eqlControllerBootRomVersion
eqlControllerBootRomVersion.description: This variable specifies the bootrom version number.

eqlControllerBootRomBuildDate.name: eqlControllerBootRomBuildDate
eqlControllerBootRomBuildDate.description: This variable specifies the date and time bootrom image was built.

eqlControllerInfoMsg.name: eqlControllerInfoMsg
eqlControllerInfoMsg.description: This variable is basic info on the cpu at bootup.

eqlControllerAthenaSataVersion.name: eqlControllerAthenaSataVersion
eqlControllerAthenaSataVersion.description: This variable is the Athena Sata revision for all Athena chips.

eqlControllerMajorVersion.name: eqlControllerMajorVersion
eqlControllerMajorVersion.description: This variable specifies the major version number of the software present on the controller module.

eqlControllerMinorVersion.name: eqlControllerMinorVersion
eqlControllerMinorVersion.description: This variable specifies the minor version number of the software present on the controller module.

eqlControllerMaintenanceVersion.name: eqlControllerMaintenanceVersion
eqlControllerMaintenanceVersion.description: This variable specifies the maintenance version number of the software present on the controller module.

eqlControllerSWCompatibilityLevel.name: eqlControllerSWCompatibilityLevel
eqlControllerSWCompatibilityLevel.description: This variable specifies the compatibility level of the software present on the controller module.

eqlControllerFullSwRevision.name: eqlControllerFullSwRevision
eqlControllerFullSwRevision.description: This variable specifies controller software revision.

eqlControllerNVRAMBattery.name: eqlControllerNVRAMBattery
eqlControllerNVRAMBattery.description: This variable represents the NVRAM Battery on CM. Value would be zero if there is no NVRAM Battery( old CM).

eqlControllerSerialNumber2.name: eqlControllerSerialNumber2
eqlControllerSerialNumber2.description: This variable specifies controller serial number. Is value of SN=.The eqlControllerSerialNumber is deprecated because this value can be upto 15 characters for manhattan.

eqlControllerType.name: eqlControllerType
eqlControllerType.description: This variable specifies the type of the controller module. Ex: Type II

eqlControllerBootTime.name: eqlControllerBootTime
eqlControllerBootTime.description: This variable specifies time at which the controller was booted expressed as seconds since epoch.

eqlBackplaneTable.name: eqlBackplaneTable
eqlBackplaneTable.description: EqualLogic-Dynamic Backplane Table. This table contains backplane status information. There is only one table entry for the one backplane per PSA.

eqlBackplaneEntry.name: eqlBackplaneEntry
eqlBackplaneEntry.description: An entry (row) containing backplane status information.

eqlBackplaneIndex.name: eqlBackplaneIndex
eqlBackplaneIndex.description: The index value that uniquely identifies the backplane. A well chosen number for the index is 1. It is in fact the only valid index.

eqlBackplanePartNum.name: eqlBackplanePartNum
eqlBackplanePartNum.description: This variable specifies part number of the backplane.

eqlBackplaneRev.name: eqlBackplaneRev
eqlBackplaneRev.description: This variable specifies revision of the backplane. Is value of Rev=

eqlBackplaneDate.name: eqlBackplaneDate
eqlBackplaneDate.description: This variable specifies date of mfg of the backplane.

eqlBackplaneSN.name: eqlBackplaneSN
eqlBackplaneSN.description: This variable specifies serial number of the backplane.

eqlBackplaneECO.name: eqlBackplaneECO
eqlBackplaneECO.description: This variable specifies eco level of the backplane.

eqlBackplaneSN2.name: eqlBackplaneSN2
eqlBackplaneSN2.description: This variable specifies the backplane serial number. Is value of SN=.The eqlBackplaneSN is deprecated because this value can be up to 15 characters for manhattan.

eqlBackplaneType.name: eqlBackplaneType
eqlBackplaneType.description: This variable specifies the backplane type.

eqlBackplaneTypeId.name: eqlBackplaneTypeId
eqlBackplaneTypeId.description: This variable specifies the backplane type as an Id. Used for Globalization.

eqlEMMTable.name: eqlEMMTable
eqlEMMTable.description: EqualLogic-Dynamic Member EMM Table. This table contains enclosure management status information. One table entry per emm. It is indexed by emm index. The number of entries is equal to the number of emms that are present in the system

eqlEMMEntry.name: eqlEMMEntry
eqlEMMEntry.description: An entry (row) containing emm status information.

eqlEMMIndex.name: eqlEMMIndex
eqlEMMIndex.description: The index value that uniquely identifies the EMM subsystem.

eqlEMMModel.name: eqlEMMModel
eqlEMMModel.description: This variable specifies controller model. Is value of Part=

eqlEMMPartNum.name: eqlEMMPartNum
eqlEMMPartNum.description: This variable specifies part number of the CM.

eqlEMMRev.name: eqlEMMRev
eqlEMMRev.description: This variable specifies revision of the CM.

eqlEMMDate.name: eqlEMMDate
eqlEMMDate.description: This variable specifies date of mfg of the CM.

eqlEMMSN.name: eqlEMMSN
eqlEMMSN.description: This variable specifies serial number of the CM.

eqlEMMECO.name: eqlEMMECO
eqlEMMECO.description: This variable specifies eco level of the CM.

eqlEMMSN2.name: eqlEMMSN2
eqlEMMSN2.description: This variable specifies the serial number. Is value of SN=.The eqlEMMSN is deprecated because this value can be up to 15 characters for manhattan.

eqlDaughterCardTable.name: eqlDaughterCardTable
eqlDaughterCardTable.description: EqualLogic-Dynamic Member DaughterCard Table. This table contains daughter card information. One table entry per daughter card. It is indexed by daughter card index. The number of entries is equal to the number of daughter cards that are present in the system

eqlDaughterCardEntry.name: eqlDaughterCardEntry
eqlDaughterCardEntry.description: An entry (row) containing daughter card information.

eqlDaughterCardIndex.name: eqlDaughterCardIndex
eqlDaughterCardIndex.description: The index value that uniquely identifies the DaughterCard subsystem. 1 based

eqlDaughterCardModel.name: eqlDaughterCardModel
eqlDaughterCardModel.description: This variable specifies controller model. Is value of Part=

eqlDaughterCardPartNum.name: eqlDaughterCardPartNum
eqlDaughterCardPartNum.description: This variable specifies part number of the daughter card.

eqlDaughterCardRev.name: eqlDaughterCardRev
eqlDaughterCardRev.description: This variable specifies revision of the daughter card.

eqlDaughterCardDate.name: eqlDaughterCardDate
eqlDaughterCardDate.description: This variable specifies date of mfg of the daughter card.

eqlDaughterCardSN.name: eqlDaughterCardSN
eqlDaughterCardSN.description: This variable specifies serial number of the daughter card.

eqlDaughterCardECO.name: eqlDaughterCardECO
eqlDaughterCardECO.description: This variable specifies eco level of the daughter card.

eqlChannelCardTable.name: eqlChannelCardTable
eqlChannelCardTable.description: EqualLogic-Dynamic Member ChannelCard Table. This table contains channel card information. One table entry per channel card. It is indexed by channel card index. The number of entries is equal to the number of channel cards that are present in the system

eqlChannelCardEntry.name: eqlChannelCardEntry
eqlChannelCardEntry.description: An entry (row) containing channel card information.

eqlChannelCardIndex.name: eqlChannelCardIndex
eqlChannelCardIndex.description: The index value that uniquely identifies the ChannelCard subsystem.

eqlChannelCardSerialNumber.name: eqlChannelCardSerialNumber
eqlChannelCardSerialNumber.description: This variable specifies serial number of the card.

eqlChannelCardFirmwareRev.name: eqlChannelCardFirmwareRev
eqlChannelCardFirmwareRev.description: This variable specifies firmware revision of the card.

eqlChannelCardInitRev.name: eqlChannelCardInitRev
eqlChannelCardInitRev.description: This variable specifies revision of the initialization configuration file.

eqlChannelCardStatus.name: eqlChannelCardStatus
eqlChannelCardStatus.description: This variable specifies the status of the channel card .

eqlSFPTable.name: eqlSFPTable
eqlSFPTable.description: EqualLogic-Dynamic Member SFP Table. This table contains SFP information. One table entry per SFP. It is indexed by SFP index. The number of entries is equal to the number of SFPs that are present in the system

eqlSFPIndex.name: eqlSFPIndex
eqlSFPIndex.description: The index value that uniquely identifies the SFP.

eqlSFPMode.name: eqlSFPMode
eqlSFPMode.description: This variable specifies the mode of the SFP.

eqlSFPIfIndex.name: eqlSFPIfIndex
eqlSFPIfIndex.description: Index of the interface attached to the SFP.

eqlSFPBitrate.name: eqlSFPBitrate
eqlSFPBitrate.description: Bit rate of the SFP in units of 100 Mbits/sec. 103 => 10300 => 10 Gbps

eqlSFPLength1.name: eqlSFPLength1
eqlSFPLength1.description: If Mode is single mode, length in kilometres, Mode is multi mode, length in units of 10metres of 50/125 um fiber.

eqlSFPLength2.name: eqlSFPLength2
eqlSFPLength2.description: If Mode is single mode, length in units of 100metres, Mode is multi mode, length in units of 10metres of 62/125 um fiber.

eqlSFPVendorName.name: eqlSFPVendorName
eqlSFPVendorName.description: This variable specifies vendor name of the SFP.

eqlSFPPartNumber.name: eqlSFPPartNumber
eqlSFPPartNumber.description: This variable specifies part number of the SFP.

eqlSFPFirmwareRev.name: eqlSFPFirmwareRev
eqlSFPFirmwareRev.description: This variable specifies firmware revision of the SFP.

eqlSFPSerialNumber.name: eqlSFPSerialNumber
eqlSFPSerialNumber.description: This variable specifies serial number of the SFP.

eqlSFPDateCode.name: eqlSFPDateCode
eqlSFPDateCode.description: This variable specifies date of manufacture of the SFP.

eqlSFPStatus.name: eqlSFPStatus
eqlSFPStatus.description: This variable specifies the status of the SFP.
